# Emacs (actual config paths)
**/***/\#*\#
**/.#*
**/*.elc

# Emacs profile caches
**/emacs/**/.cache/
**/emacs/**/elpa/
**/emacs/**/eln-cache/
**/emacs/**/straight/
**/emacs/**/var/
**/emacs/**/gptel/
**/emacs/**/tree-sitter/
**/emacs/**/etc/

# Vim (anywhere in tree)
**/[._]*.s[a-v][a-z]
**/[._]*.sw[a-p]
**/[._]s[a-rt-v][a-z]
**/[._]ss[a-gi-z]
**/[._]sw[a-p]
**/Session.vim
**/.netrwhist

# macOS (anywhere in tree)
**/.DS_Store
**/.AppleDouble
**/.LSOverride
**/._*

# Windows (anywhere in tree)
**/Thumbs.db
**/ehthumbs.db
**/Desktop.ini
**/$RECYCLE.BIN/

# Linux (anywhere in tree)
**/.fuse_hidden*
**/.directory
**/.Trash-*

# IDE (anywhere in tree)
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# Build artifacts
**/*.o
**/*.a
**/*.so
**/*.pyc
**/__pycache__/

# Temporary files
**/*.tmp
**/*.log
**/*.bak
